Start : 17May2025

2:45 - Intro/Install ============================================================================================================================================================================= 
npx create-next-app@latest goat-notes # creates a next app with yes to these options : Typescript, Eslint, Tailwind, '/src', App Router, Turbopack - No to Import Alias customize
cd goatnotes
npm run dev 
Start cleaning everything out of the 'layout.tsx' 'page.tsx', etc
'rfce' # Install ES7+ React/Redux/React-Native snippets extension from dsznajder
npm add -D prettier prettier-plugin-tailwindcss # autosorting for tailwind
"react/no-unescaped-entities": "off", # will allow you to use commas / apostrophes 
https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/installation/next
npx shadcn@latest init #initialize shadcn to project
npm install next-themes #add dark mode to project from shadcn
npx shadcn@latest add toast #deprecated, used sonner instead
npx shadcn@latest add sonner # added this, he said toast is going to be used, future sean just needs to remember to replace toast with sonner
Had to install prettier, 'Ctrl' + 'Shift' + 'P' = to add prettier to user settings JSON config

